biotools.summary:
U-Net Model for Brain Extraction on Non-human Primates.

U-Net model and PRIME-DE skull-stripped brain masks (pre-release).

This is a pre-release of skull-stripped brian masks of T1w images for 136 macaque monkeys (20 sites) from PRIME-DE. The masks are created from a convolutional network - UNet model, initially trained on a human sample and upgraded with macaque data.
